// Features
// Create Projects — Users can add new projects to the board.
// Create and Assign Tasks — Create tasks and assign them to participants within the project.
// Task Status Management — Drag & drop tasks between statuses like To Do, In Progress, and Completed.
// Attractive and Clean UI — Modern, responsive, and intuitive design for a better user experience.
// User Authentication — Secure signup and login system.
// Comment and Activity Log — Keep track of task updates and participant comments (if included).
